<h2>东莞一保安4年写60万字小说 每天下班写作四五个小时</h2>
<div class="infos">
<span class="tm">04-22 08:01</span>
<span class="source">来源:<a href="http://www.nandu.com" target="_blank">南方都市报</a>
</span>
<div class="shares">
<div class="bdsharebuttonbox" data-tag="share_1">
